title: The Cockatoo's Story
description: Mrs. George, Anne Jane Cupples, nee Douglas (1839-1898) was the author Bluff Crag; or, A Good Word Costs Nothing (1872), Carry's Rose; or, The Magic of Kindness (1881), The Cockatoo's Story (1881), Talks with Uncle Richard About Wild Animals and Mamma's Stories About Domestic Pets.
author: Anne Jane Cupples
